					</div>
					<div id="dsq-comment-body-227948" class="dsq-comment-body">
						<div id="dsq-comment-message-227948" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Shorter workouts definitely worked well for me. To start with, it&#8217;s better to just to do the exercise, regardless of how long you do it for. Of course, when it&#8217;s become an <a href="http://www.mallosworld.co.uk/organize-it/2007/09/10/habit-building-laying-the-foundations/" rel="nofollow">habit</a>, then you can start thinking about setting targets and goals as you know you won&#8217;t end up putting yourself off getting the exercise.</p>
